{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"Maatsii Realtime Chart Frames API (Canonical c1..c200, Zero-Cache, ChatGPT-Optimized)","version":"7.3.0-chatgpt","description":"Maatsii serves realtime annotated TradingView chart frames (JPEG, 720x1280) for 200 financial charts across futures, commodities, crypto, FX, rates/credit, volatility, ratios, and equities.\n\nOPTIMIZED FOR CHATGPT / OPENAI ACTIONS:\n- This API is image-first: the primary action is fetching a fresh JPEG frame for a given canonical chart id.\n- LLM-side caching is the main failure mode: clients may reuse prior image responses unless every request is uniquely cache-busted.\n\nCRITICAL REALTIME REQUIREMENT:\n- Charts update frequently; frames must be treated as ephemeral.\n- Client MUST fetch a fresh URL each time the user asks for an updated frame.\n- ALWAYS append a unique cachebuster query param on every request: ?cb={unique}\n- Use a random string or incrementing counter (timestamps may collide).\n- DO NOT reuse previously requested URLs.\n- Server returns no-cache response headers to discourage downstream caching.\n- Freshness is visually verifiable (timestamp/annotation embedded in pixels).\n\nCANONICAL IDENTIFIERS ONLY:\n- Use lowercase c1..c200 only.\n\nDiscovery:\n- Human docs: https://api.maatsii.com/llms.txt\n- Machine schema: https://api.maatsii.com/openapi.json","contact":{"name":"Maatsii API Support","url":"https://api.maatsii.com","email":"api@maatsii.com"},"x-logo":{"url":"https://api.maatsii.com/logo.png"},"x-related-documentation":{"aiAgentDiscovery":"https://api.maatsii.com/llms.txt","humanReadable":"https://api.maatsii.com/llm.txt","canonicalSchema":"https://api.maatsii.com/openapi.json"}},"servers":[{"url":"https://api.maatsii.com","description":"Production (Cloudflare configured for zero-cache on frame endpoints)"}],"tags":[{"name":"Frames","description":"Realtime binary JPEG chart frames (canonical c1..c200)."},{"name":"System","description":"Health and diagnostics."}],"paths":{"/{id}.